s/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">出糧換美金 全民提款日</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">9.07 機場交通測試 13:00</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">9.08 美國人權及民主法案大遊行 14:00</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">9.13 各區同慶賀中秋 人鏈 19:00 - 22:00</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">9.14 機場交通測試 13:00</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">轉頭見</span></span></div><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">五大訴求 缺一不可</span></div>"},{"pid":"b1dd5eb6cfd4b7e4bc9d60fd8d4a4d12decd41fc","tid":1534534,"uid":22624,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T05:16:52.000Z","msg":"好正常，香港人都已經唔識上幾代啲鄉下話，人地已經係加拿大人"},{"pid":"ed29dceafa45c16b74abaa7b6ebf4d1a099d6151","tid":1534534,"uid":133525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T05:17:30.000Z","msg":"屌，你而家先知呀？"},{"pid":"5683a6eb3384db2f16ae282ff408bdea65112874","tid":1534534,"uid":289649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T05:19:07.000Z","msg":"明白大家呢排嘅士氣經過<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">831恐襲</span></span>同<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">901大撤退</span></span>之後好低落<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我同大家一樣都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但越係呢啲時候<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">我地就越要堅持下去，<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">團結一致</span></span><br />\n唔好比林鄭見我地冇士氣而去捉多啲人<br />\n<br />\n以下兩篇文章<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">無論<span style=\"color: gold;\">和理非</span>，定係<span style=\"color: red;\">勇武</span>，都應該入黎，打返枝<span style=\"color: violet;\">強心針</span></span><br />\n<br />\n希望可以幫到大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n記得share比身邊因近日事件而唔開心嘅朋友仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/on_hold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n［全部人同我入黎］《致眾表》望各位香港市民出自己的一份綿力<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1532967\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1532967</a><br />\n<br />\n灰心喪志，是因為你看不見抗爭的前路<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1533741\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1533741</a>"},{"pid":"c2b2bd9d33bd2f08903e164cfe4b37401d94528b","tid":1534534,"uid":202464,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T05:20:03.000Z","msg":"人地係土生土長加拿大人。點解要識廣東話？"},{"pid":"ce835d089769f67bf141938eb97f81349885f0c7","tid":1534534,"uid":33668,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b1dd5eb6cfd4b7e4bc9d60fd8d4a4d12decd41fc","tid":1534534,"uid":22624,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T05:16:52.000Z","msg":"好正常，香港人都已經唔識上幾代啲鄉下話，人地已經係加拿大人"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T05:20:41.000Z","msg":"認同<br />\n識講普通話仲做大中華膠果d最可恥"},{"pid":"c4ba029d89670f9581714b52f7d18987c0dcc938","tid":1534534,"uid":82706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T14:23:40.000Z","msg":"其實我呀爺呀嫲都咁睇我地嗰代<br />\n佢地台山人，我老豆識講台山話但廣東話<br />\n去到我嗰代台山話已經消失咗"},{"pid":"1cd8fcbbcd90cd917bed1b8c2c9b446880f2359c","tid":1534534,"uid":34828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T14:24:38.000Z","msg":"咁咪好囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}